io.netty.channel

接口 ChannelProgressivePromise

  • 所有超级接口:
    ChannelFuture, ChannelProgressiveFuture, ChannelPromise, Future<Void>, ProgressiveFuture<Void>, ProgressivePromise<Void>, Promise<Void>
    所有已知实现类:
    DefaultChannelProgressivePromise

    public interface ChannelProgressivePromise
extends ProgressivePromise<Void>, ChannelProgressiveFuture, ChannelPromise
    Special ChannelPromise which will be notified once the associated bytes is transferring.
